I’ve validated the main new signals in code: the Curve V2 liquidation precheck bug, three reward-accounting flaws (stale accumulator, claim-window sniping, migration claim gap), ETH/WETH LP withdraw-manager mismatch, Ethena pending valuation drift, and Morpho migration rounding risk all have concrete implementation support. I’m now finalizing keep/reject decisions and building the merged JSON list with deduplicated IDs.
